---
title: Annotation Author Name
section: developers
---

Starting with [PSPDFKit for iOS 4][], we will ask for the author name before the first annotation is created.

This behavior can be disabled via setting [`shouldAskForAnnotationUsername`][] to `NO` in [`PSPDFConfiguration`][].

PSPDFKit uses various heuristics to suggest a suitable default name.

You can always change the default value for a [`PSPDFDocument`][] by customizing [`defaultAnnotationUsername`][].

